125
00:09:33.657 --> 00:09:34.824
Aku takut, Mo.

126
00:09:37.328 --> 00:09:39.913
Meggie, aku akan menjagamu.

127
00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:42.373
Aku selalu menjagamu.

128
00:09:44.210 --> 00:09:45.835
